4. Only then commit to the JSON output.

Your internal deliberation is your private workspace — use it fully. \
Your JSON output is final; resolve all ambiguity before committing to it. \
Do NOT emit a classification that you are not internally certain about.

## Output schema — IMPORTANT

You communicate with three JSON responses ONLY. Output raw JSON with no surrounding text.

